name: Training Courses - Become A Certified Ghoststar Agent
description:
Become a Trained and Certified Ghoststar Agent.

With over 12 different hands on courses you will become a trained and certified Ghoststar Agent in just a matter of weeks.

This program is not for the weak at heart. This is a tough, demanding, in your face training course. 

For more information please email us with the subject "I Want To Become A Ghoststar Agent"

name: Official Ghoststar Special Agent Badge
description:
The Official Ghoststar Special Agent Badge is issued only to Trained and Certified Ghoststar Special Agents. 

Please include your Ghoststar Agent ID number, full name, date of birth, and address in the order detail.

name: Official Ghoststar Fugative Recovery Started Kit
description:
The Official Ghoststar Fugative Recovery Agent Starter Kit is issued only to Trained and Certified Ghoststar Fugative Recovery Agents.

Please include your Ghoststar Agent ID number, full name, date of birth, and address in the order detail.

name: Official Ghoststar Fugative Recovery Agent Patch
description:
The Official Ghoststar Fugative Recovery Agent Transferable patch is issued only to Trained and Certified Ghoststar Fugative Recovery Agents.

Please include your Ghoststar Agent ID number, full name, date of birth, and address in the order detail. 

12 inches by 5 inches.

name: Official Ghoststar Security Enforcement Window I.D
description:
The Official Ghoststar Security Enforcement Window I.D is needed when any Certified/Trained Ghoststar Agent is on a detail.

Every agent must possess one of these. 

Please include your Ghoststar Agent ID number, full name, date of birth, and address in the order detail.

name: Official Ghoststar Security Officer Window I.D
description:

name: Official Ghoststar Certified Agent Pen - Set of 12
description:
The Official Ghoststar Certified Agent Pen. 

This pen not only shows the rank of being a Registered Ghoststar Agent, it also doubles as a form of protection.

Embedded with a small 3 inch blade, discretely placed in the upper half of the pen.

Set of 12.

name: COSMIC FORCE FREQUENCY GLOVES
description:
Negative frequencies are damaging your body's equilibrium. As pioneers of this new technology we have developed a process of restoring balance to your body's natural chemistry through a sequence of embedding healthy frequencies into our patented gloves.

Perfect glove for any hardcore sport, motorcycle riding, or any day to day work.

name: Holy Ghoststar Power Stakes
description:
Genuine hardwood Ghoststar vampire stakes are handmade in America by a Ghoststar master craftsman.

Approx. 14 inches overall length.

Display stand included.

Vampire stake and display stand available in your choice of finish.

name: Executive Polo B/W
description:
These Ghoststar executive polo's are made out of 100% cotton. 

They have the Ghoststar logo embroidered on the front left. Along with the name Ghoststar embroidered on the left sleeve.

Look great while playing golf, in the office, or while riding your motorcycle in one of these executive polo's!
